###  Quantitative Evaluation
| Fusion Case          | MSE   | PSNR (dB) | SSIM |
|----------------------|-------|-----------|------|
| T1ce + T2            | 0.021 | 34.7      | 0.89 |
| T1ce + FLAIR         | 0.018 | 35.1      | 0.90 |
| T1ce + T2 + FLAIR    | 0.015 | 36.4      | 0.92 |

>  Metrics are computed against **T1ce** as the reference image.  
> Images are resized to 256Ã—256 and normalized before fusion.
